---
<div class="text-left border-2 rounded-2xl mt-10 p-10 mx-40 bg-secondarybackground border-accent dark:bg-secondarybackground-dark dark:border-accent-dark">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-5">My Development Stack</h1>
    <p class="mb-5">Here are some technologies I work with:</p>
    <ul class="grid grid-cols-3 grid-rows-2 flex-wrap gap-4 text-xl justify-content-center text-center">
        <li class="border rounded-lg p-4 border-accent">HTML</li>
        <li class="border rounded-lg p-4 border-accent">Python</li>
        <li class="border rounded-lg p-4 border-accent">TypeScript</li>
        <li class="border rounded-lg p-4 border-accent">React</li>
        <li class="border rounded-lg p-4 border-accent">Astro</li>
        <li class="border rounded-lg p-4 border-accent">Tailwind CSS</li>
    </ul>
</div>